  "text": "The theme safe situation was identified related to the environmental factors of debriefing (where). The theme represents a nonthreatening, trusting environment for debriefing, which was often highlighted in the nursing education literature. According to Table 3 , three papers highlighted the importance of ensuring the safe environment for participants to engage in debriefing. One paper [CITATION_1] presented data on participants' preference for a safe environment. Yet the paper was coded to \"neutral\" as there was insufficient evidence to conclude this participant preference.",
